{"title":"前端三剑客: HTML/CSS/JavaScript","uid":"004992c1c97a2410f49880be41043864","slug":"前端三剑客-HTML-CSS-JavaScript","date":"2024-01-27T02:55:51.000Z","updated":"2024-01-27T12:48:58.499Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/前端三剑客-HTML-CSS-JavaScript.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h3 id=\"HTML-结构\"><a href=\"#HTML-结构\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HTML:结构\"></a>HTML:结构</h3><ul>\n<li><p>HTML是一种<strong>超文本标记</strong>语言，不是一种编程语言</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>主要用来实现静态页面，我们在页面看到的文本，图片，视频，声音，表格，链接等都是通过HTML语言描述的</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>HTML的是由标签组成，给不同的标签不同的属性，可以实现不同的网页效果。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>页面基本结构:</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;!</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">DOCTYPE</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">meta</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">charset</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">UTF-8</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">页面标题</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">一个标题</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">p</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">一个段落</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">p</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>参考手册: <a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/tags/ref-byfunc.html\">HTML 标签列表（功能排序） | 菜鸟教程 </a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"CSS-修饰\"><a href=\"#CSS-修饰\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CSS:修饰\"></a>CSS:修饰</h3><h4 id=\"介绍\"><a href=\"#介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"介绍\"></a>介绍</h4><ul>\n<li>CSS 用于 HTML 文档中元素样式的定义</li>\n<li>使用 CSS 的目的就是让网页具有美观一致的页面</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"参考手册\"><a href=\"#参考手册\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考手册\"></a>参考手册</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/cssref/css-reference.html\">CSS 参考手册 | 菜鸟教程 (runoob.com)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"基础语法\"><a href=\"#基础语法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础语法\"></a>基础语法</h4><h5 id=\"选择器\"><a href=\"#选择器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"选择器\"></a>选择器</h5><ul>\n<li><p><strong>元素选择器</strong>：选择特定类型的元素，如 <code>p</code> 表示段落。</p>\n<div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">input</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">width</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">250px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">padding</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">10px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">margin-bottom</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">10px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">1px</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> solid </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">bfbcbc</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border-radius</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">4px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>使用示例:</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">input</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">type</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">text</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">phoneNumber</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">name</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">phoneNumber</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">required</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>使用前:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/xGiWH.png\"></p>\n<p>使用后: 可以看到输入框(input)改变了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/xGjeD.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>类选择器</strong>：选择具有特定类的元素，如 <code>.highlight</code> 表示具有 <code>highlight</code> 类的元素。</p>\n<div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">textStyle</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">text-align</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> center</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">/*仅一级标题(h1)能够使用*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">/*如果直接写  .textStyle , 所有元素都可以使用*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>使用示例: </p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">class</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">textStyle</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">模拟登录</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>使用前:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/xGdu5.png\"></p>\n<p>使用后: 可以看到, 标题文字被居中<br><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/xG88s.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>ID选择器</strong>：选择具有特定ID的元素，如 <code>#header</code> 表示具有 <code>header</code> ID 的元素。</p>\n<div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">loginForm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">width</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">300px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">margin</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> auto</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">padding</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">20px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">1px</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> solid </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">6e6c6c</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border-radius</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">5px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>使用示例:</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">form</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">loginForm</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">label</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">for</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">phoneNumber</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">手机号：</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">label</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">input</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">type</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">text</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">phoneNumber</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">name</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">phoneNumber</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">required</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">type</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">submit</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">登录</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">form</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>使用前:<br><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/xGYpA.png\"></p>\n<p>使用后: 可以看到, 整个表单的属性改变了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/xGjeD.png\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"CSS创建\"><a href=\"#CSS创建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CSS创建\"></a>CSS创建</h5><ul>\n<li><p>内部样式表: 在html文件头部(<head>)用<style>定义样式表, 例如:</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">meta</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">charset</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">UTF-8</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">模拟登录</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">style</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">loginForm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">            </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">width</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">300px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">            </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">margin</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> auto</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">            </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">padding</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">20px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">            </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">1px</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> solid </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">6e6c6c</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">            </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border-radius</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">5px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        &lt;!--省略其他选择器--</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">style</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>外部样式表: 将样式表保存在外部文件中, 在html的<head>中使用<link>链接到样式表, 例如</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">meta</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">charset</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">UTF-8</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">模拟登录</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">link</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">rel</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">stylesheet</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">href</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">style/test1.css</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>style&#x2F;test1.css:</p>\n<div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">loginForm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">     </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">width</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">300px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">     </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">margin</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> auto</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">     </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">padding</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">20px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">     </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">1px</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> solid </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">6e6c6c</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">     </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border-radius</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">5px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">input</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">width</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">250px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">padding</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">10px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">margin-bottom</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">10px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">1px</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> solid </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">#</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">bfbcbc</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">border-radius</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">4px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">textStyle</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B2CCD6\">text-align</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> center</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">\t</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>内联样式: 在相关的标签内直接使用样式（style）属性, 例如</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">p</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">style</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">color:sienna;margin-left:20px</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">这是一个段落。</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">p</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p><em>慎用, 建议只在一个元素上使用一次时使用</em></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>多重样式优先级: 内联 &gt; 内部 &gt; 外部 &gt; 浏览器默认</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"JavaScript-行动\"><a href=\"#JavaScript-行动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"JavaScript:行动\"></a>JavaScript:行动</h3><h4 id=\"介绍-1\"><a href=\"#介绍-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"介绍\"></a>介绍</h4><ul>\n<li><p>JavaScript是一门<strong>轻量级</strong>的脚本语言，是一种运行在<strong>客户端</strong>的脚本语言 </p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Script 是脚本的意思</p>\n<p>脚本语言：不需要编译，运行过程中由 js 解释器(js 引擎）逐行来进行解释并执行</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>不同于Java程序运行在JVM中，JavaScript运行是直接运行在浏览器中</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>主要使用来实现<strong>页面功能</strong>和<strong>业务逻辑</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"参考手册-1\"><a href=\"#参考手册-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考手册\"></a>参考手册</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/jsref/jsref-tutorial.html\">JavaScript 和 HTML DOM 参考手册 | 菜鸟教程 (runoob.com)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"基础作用\"><a href=\"#基础作用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础作用\"></a>基础作用</h4><ul>\n<li><p>直接写入 HTML 输出流</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>对事件的响应</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>改变 HTML 内容, 图像, 样式</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>验证输入</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"JavaScript使用\"><a href=\"#JavaScript使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"JavaScript使用\"></a>JavaScript使用</h4><ul>\n<li><p>HTML中的 JS 代码必须在<script>标签中,   可以在<head>或<body>部分中, 例如:</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;!</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">DOCTYPE</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">lang</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zh-CN</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">meta</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">charset</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">utf-8</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">learn01</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">            document</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">write</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hello world!</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>效果: </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/xyXA5.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>函数</strong>: 在触发某种事件的时候可以调用函数, 以实现某些交互效果, 例如:</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;!</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">DOCTYPE</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">lang</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">en</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">meta</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">charset</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">UTF-8</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">meta</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">name</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">viewport</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">content</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">Document</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">function</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">test</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">()</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #F07178\">            </span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">document</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">getElementById</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">demo</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">innerHTML</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">Hello world!</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #F07178\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">p</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">demo</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        一个段落</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">p</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">type</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">onclick</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">test</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">()</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">        点我</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>点击后, 页面会出现一些变化</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/KVi4J.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/KVUbV.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>外部的JavaScript</strong>:在<script>标签的\"src\"属性中设置 JS 文件的路径, 例如:</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">src</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">script/script01.js</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"输出\"><a href=\"#输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出\"></a>输出</h4><ul>\n<li><strong>显示数据</strong>:<ul>\n<li>使用 <strong>window.alert()</strong> 弹出警告框。</li>\n<li>使用 <strong>document.write()</strong> 方法将内容写到 HTML 文档中。</li>\n<li>使用 <strong>innerHTML</strong> 写入到 HTML 元素。</li>\n<li>使用 <strong>console.log()</strong> 写入到浏览器的控制台。在Console菜单中</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>操作HTML元素</strong>: 用\"id\"属性<strong>标识</strong>元素, 用<code>document.getElementById(id) </code>方法查找该元素, 使用<code>innerHTML()</code>来获取或插入元素内容, 如上</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"事件\"><a href=\"#事件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"事件\"></a>事件</h4><ul>\n<li><p>HTML 事件可以是浏览器行为，也可以是用户行为, 实例：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTML 页面完成加载</li>\n<li>HTML input 字段改变时</li>\n<li>HTML 按钮被点击</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>事件手册: <a href=\"https://www.w3school.com.cn/tags/html_ref_eventattributes.asp\">HTML 事件参考手册</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>触发时调用 JS :</p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">some-HTML-element</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">some-event</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">JavaScript 代码</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>例如: </p>\n<div class=\"language-html\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">html</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">type</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">onclick</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;this.</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">innerHTML</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\"> </span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">Date</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">()</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">Time</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">button</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>点击后(触发\"onclick\"事件)会显示当前时间</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/KFAGl.png\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"JavaScript-DOM\"><a href=\"#JavaScript-DOM\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"JavaScript DOM\"></a>JavaScript DOM</h4><ul>\n<li>DOM : Document Object Model, 文档对象模型</li>\n<li>通过HTML DOM, JavaScript能够创建动态HTML, 效果如上(Hello world例子)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3school.com.cn/js/js_htmldom.asp\">JavaScript HTML DOM</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"JavaScript-BOM\"><a href=\"#JavaScript-BOM\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"JavaScript BOM\"></a>JavaScript BOM</h4><ul>\n<li><p>BOM: Browser Object Model,  浏览器对象模型</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>简单来说，它就是操作控制浏览器的一种能力，工具, 如获取浏览器信息, 前进, 后退页面, 弹出窗口等</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>一些基本的形式:<br><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/KF6WW.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/27/KFWev.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://www.w3school.com.cn/js/js_window.asp\">JavaScript Window - 浏览器对象模型</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","feature":true,"text":"HTML:结构 HTML是一种超文本标记语言，不是一种编程语言 主要用来实现静态页面，我们在页面看到的文本，图片，视频，声音，表格，链接等都是通过HTML语言描...","permalink":"/post/前端三剑客-HTML-CSS-JavaScript","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.1k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"学习日志","slug":"学习日志","count":6,"path":"api/tags/学习日志.json"},{"name":"前端基础","slug":"前端基础","count":1,"path":"api/tags/前端基础.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#HTML-%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">HTML:结构</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CSS-%E4%BF%AE%E9%A5%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CSS:修饰</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">介绍</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E6%89%